headline: 3 Consumer Stocks with Questionable Fundamentals
summary: The performance of consumer discretionary businesses is closely linked to economic cycles. Over the past six months, it seems like demand trends are working against their favor as the industry has tumbled by 1.8%. This drawdown was disheartening since the S&P 500 gained 4.7%.
